urce/Emitter-coupled_logic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emitter-coupled_logic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aston Villa's Europa Conference League run ended at the semi-final stage, as opponents, Olympiakos set up a final with Fiorentina.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4065291100604787e-12, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 218, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.100579550450193e-35, \"text\": \"Conference League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\"}, {\"begin\": 285, \"end\": 295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999993037818, \"rank\": 4.153796972720443e-10, \"text\": \"Olympiakos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5252274224604105e-18, \"text\": \"Fiorentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having lost the first leg 4-2, Aston Villa fell to a 2-0 defeat in Greece to lose their tie 6-2 on aggregate.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4065291100604787e-12, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999563443, \"rank\": 4.321208425373536e-11, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi, who scored a hat-trick in the first leg, scored the two goals for the host.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to TNT Sports after the game, Emery said his team controlled the game, but were not clinical.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.277191017564826e-22, \"text\": \"TNT Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\", \"score\": 0.9999999983610905, \"rank\": 1.6388297787064391e-09, \"text\": \"Emery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We got to be in Europe at the end of last season and this year we enjoyed it, but to win is very difficult and we are in the process [of developing],\\\" Emery said.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They [Olympiakos] deserve to be in the final.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We lost it in the first 90 minutes at home and we were not competitive.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We started this first half well, they scored but we controlled the game, but we were not clinical.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is an experience for us at Aston Villa after a long time [of not being in Europe] and again we are going to compete in Europe next year.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course we are a little bit disappointed, a little bit frustrated but we have to move on quickly.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We started the first leg and maybe we were favourites but after the first leg, we were not.\\\"\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Transfer: 'They are pushing, he's top priority' - Romano names player Arsenal want to sign  I am very calm - Vinicius Jr speaks on winning 2024 Ballon d'Or  EPL: Wes Brown criticizes Sesko after Man Utd's 3-1 win over Aston Villa  EPL: Man Utd seek revenge against Aston Villa in battle for Champions League spot  EPL: Chris Sutton predicts Man Utd vs Aston Villa, Chelsea against Newcastle, others  Paul Merson predicts Man Utd vs Aston Villa, Chelsea against Newcastle, others  EPL: Paul Merson predicts Aston Villa vs Chelsea, Man Utd, Arsenal, other fixtures  EPL: Arokodare cleared to face Aston Villa after racist attack  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1469, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinicius_de_Moraes\", \"